type: software
title: "Claude Ads"
abstract: >
  Free-first paid advertising audit and optimization skill for Claude Code,
  focused on the 3 platforms where 95% of advertiser spend lives: Meta, Google,
  TikTok. ~158 weighted audit checks (Meta 50 + Google 80 incl YouTube video
  campaigns + TikTok 28), industry-specific templates, parallel subagent
  delegation, hybrid MCP+API+manual data tiers, /ads update for refreshing
  platform references with the last 30 days of changes, and from v2.4.0 a
  guided first-run wizard (/ads start) + continuous coach (/ads next) with
  persistent profile + audit history.
